Hello.
Hello
Hello, how can I help?
I am interested in going to view an apartment at Shady Apartments.
You suddenly remember that you have a hot date on Wednesday at 11 am. [instruction 2 of 6]
What is your name?
Could you give me your name, please?
Yes, my name is Mark.
Ask something about the apartment, or engage in smalltalk, or make a joke. [instruction 3 of 6]
What day
What day would you like to make the booking for?
I would have liked to go on Wednesday at 11 am, but I have a date that I've been looking forward to. It's a hot one.

You cannot remember if you had payed the application fee. Find a way to make an appointment anyway. If no date is available, change date and/or time until something works. If you already got the appointment, engage in smalltalk. [instruction 4 of 6]
What time would you like it to start?

Well, I can't remember if I paid the application fee, but I would really like to see this apartment because I have heard great things from the residents.
Once you've scheduled the viewing, say something about your hot date. [instruction 5 of 6]
